Package: streamsampler
Title: Characterize and Subsample Stream Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
    given = "Kyle", family = "Hurley", 
    email = "khurley@usgs.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-6469-3769")), 
    person(
    given = "Jeff", family = "Chanat", 
    email = "jchanat@usgs.gov", role = c("aut"), 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3629-7307")))
Description: A series of functions that characterizes daily stream discharge and water quality data 
    and subsamples the water quality data. Provide dates, discharge, and water quality measurements 
    and `streamsampler` can find gaps, get summary statistics, and subsample according to common 
    stream sampling protocols.
